type.description:
## Self Action On Kill

---



[Power Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/power_types/self_action_on_kill)

Executes an [Entity Action Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/power_types/self_action_on_kill) on the entity that has the power when the entity kills another entity.

Type ID: `origins:self_action_on_kill`




---

### Examples

```json
{
    "type": "origins:self_action_on_kill",
    "entity_action": {
        "type": "origins:heal",
        "amount": 4.0
    },
    "cooldown": 100,
    "hud_render": {
        "should_render": true,
        "sprite_location": "origins:textures/gui/community/spiderkolo/resource_bar_01.png",
        "bar_index": 5
    },
    "condition": {
        "type": "origins:equipped_item",
        "equipment_slot": "mainhand",
        "item_condition": {
            "type": "origins:ingredient",
            "ingredient": {
                "item": "minecraft:iron_sword"
            }
        }
    }
}
```

This example will restore 2 hearts to the entity that has the power if the entity has killed a mob with an Iron Sword.

